Package: vog
Title: Van Oirbeek's Grammar - A Unified Framework for Claims Reserving
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Robin", "Van Oirbeek", , "robin.vanoirbeek@uantwerpen.be", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Implements a unified framework for claims reserving in non-life insurance,
    including the Negative Binomial Chain-Ladder (NB-CL) model. Provides a full 
    likelihood framework for claim count triangles with functions for model fitting, 
    prediction, parametric bootstrap with REML-like bias correction, diagnostics, 
    and model comparison.
